input: what is the body weight change of patient 006-161415 last measured on the first hospital visit compared to the second to last value measured on the first hospital visit?
predict:
WITH patient_weights AS (
    SELECT 
        p.uniquepid,
        p.patienthealthsystemstayid,
        p.hospitaladmittime,
        p.admissionweight,
        p.dischargeweight,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY p.uniquepid ORDER BY p.hospitaladmittime) as visit_rank
    FROM patient p
    WHERE p.uniquepid = '006-161415'
),
first_visit AS (
    SELECT *
    FROM patient_weights
    WHERE visit_rank = 1
),
weight_values AS (
    SELECT 
        admissionweight as weight_value,
        hospitaladmittime as weight_time,
        1 as weight_order
    FROM first_visit
    WHERE admissionweight IS NOT NULL
    
    UNION ALL
    
    SELECT 
        dischargeweight as weight_value,
        hospitaladmittime as weight_time,
        2 as weight_order
    FROM first_visit
    WHERE dischargeweight IS NOT NULL
),
ordered_weights AS (
    SELECT 
        weight_value,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY weight_order, weight_time) as position,
        COUNT(*) OVER () as total_count
    FROM weight_values
)
SELECT 
    (SELECT weight_value FROM ordered_weights WHERE position = total_count) -
    (SELECT weight_value FROM ordered_weights WHERE position = total_count - 1) as weight_change

WITH urine_alkalinization_patients AS (
    SELECT 
        p.patientunitstayid,
        p.uniquepid,
        m.drugstarttime,
        EXTRACT(YEAR FROM m.drugstarttime) as year,
        EXTRACT(MONTH FROM m.drugstarttime) as month
    FROM patient p
    JOIN medication m ON p.patientunitstayid = m.patientunitstayid
    WHERE m.drugname LIKE '%sodium bicarbonate%'
        AND m.drugstarttime >= '2104-01-01'
),
subsequent_treatments AS (
    SELECT 
        t.treatmentname,
        COUNT(*) as procedure_count
    FROM urine_alkalinization_patients uap

        AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM t.treatmenttime) = uap.month
        AND t.treatmenttime >= uap.drugstarttime
    GROUP BY t.treatmentname
)
SELECT 
    treatmentname,
    procedure_count
FROM subsequent_treatments
ORDER BY procedure_count DESC
LIMIT 3;

AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM l.labresulttime) = EXTRACT(MONTH FROM d.diagnosistime)

ORDER BY frequency DESC

input: tell me the top three most frequent specimens that patients were tested in the same month after receiving thyroid hormone - injection in 2105.
predict:
WITH thyroid_treatments AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT 
        t.patientunitstayid,
        DATE_TRUNC('month', t.treatmenttime) as treatment_month
    FROM treatment t
    WHERE LOWER(t.treatmentname) LIKE '%thyroid hormone%' 
        AND LOWER(t.treatmentname) LIKE '%injection%'
        AND EXTRACT(year FROM t.treatmenttime) = 2105
),
cultures_after_treatment AS (
    SELECT 
        m.culturesite,
        COUNT(*) as specimen_count
    FROM microlab m

    WHERE DATE_TRUNC('month', m.culturetakentime) >= tt.treatment_month
        AND DATE_TRUNC('month', m.culturetakentime) = tt.treatment_month
    GROUP BY m.culturesite
)
SELECT culturesite, specimen_count
FROM cultures_after_treatment
ORDER BY specimen_count DESC
LIMIT 3;
